menu "KitchenSync Configuration"

    config KS_WIFI_SSID
        string "WiFi SSID"
        default ""
        help
            SSID of the WiFi network to join (same network as the Ableton Link
            session). Left empty in the repo — set it locally (menuconfig or a
            gitignored sdkconfig); do not commit credentials.

    config KS_WIFI_PASSWORD
        string "WiFi Password"
        default ""
        help
            Password for the WiFi network. Set locally; do not commit.

    config KS_TOUCH_DISPLAY
        bool "Enable the 1.47\" touch LCD (Waveshare S3-Touch-LCD-1.47)"
        depends on IDF_TARGET_ESP32S3
        default n
        help
            ESP-026 spike: drive the KitchenSync Touch 1.47" LCD + AXS5106L touch from
            this ESP-IDF firmware (see ks_display.cpp). S3-only — the panel exists on the
            Waveshare S3-Touch-LCD board; a headless S3 (Super Mini) leaves this off.
            Pulls in the LovyanGFX managed component (idf_component.yml, S3 target only).

endmenu
